
'''Nathalie Mpaka''', ni umucungamari akaba n'umuyobozi mukuru muri BK Group Plc (yahoze ari [[Banki ya Kigali]] ), banki nini y'ubucuruzi mu [[Rwanda]] . Ni umuyobozi mukuru ushinzwe imari muri BK Group. <ref name="1R">https://www.theeastafrican.co.ke/business/Bank-of-Kigali-net-profit-up-17pc/2560-5047632-ejsilr/index.html</ref>

== Uburezi ==
Madamu Mpaka afite impamyabumenyi ihanitse y’ubuhanzi mu icungamari  yakuye muri kaminuza ya Birmingham City, i Birmingham, mu [[Bwongereza]], mu 2006. Ni n'umucungamari wemewe, wemewe na Association of Chartered Certified Accountants (ACCA), bo mu [[Ubwongereza|Bwongereza]] . <ref name="2R">https://www.linkedin.com/in/nathalie-mpaka-497aba17/</ref> Byongeye kandi, ni umunyamuryango w'Ikigo gishinzwe ibaruramari ryemewe mu [[Rwanda]] (ICPAR). <ref name="3R">https://www.bkgi.rw/about-us/board-of-directors</ref>

== Umwuga ==
Mu gihe yari akiri umunyeshuri wa kaminuza hagati ya 2004 na 2006, Nathalie yakoraga nk'umucungamari wungirije muri Parkwood Leisure Limited, isosiyete ikorera i Worcester mu Bwongereza, nko mu 50 kilometres (31 mi), mu majyepfo y'uburengerazuba bw'umujyi wa Birmingham. Yaje guhabwa akazi nk'umucungamari wemewe, na White Stuff Clothing, ihuriro ry'amaduka arenga 115 mu [[Bwongereza]], ahakorera imyaka itanu kuva 2007 kugeza 2012. <ref name="2R">{{Template:Cite web}}<cite class="citation web cs1" data-ve-ignore="true" id="CITEREFNathalie_Mpaka2019">Nathalie Mpaka (2019). [https://www.linkedin.com/in/nathalie-mpaka-497aba17/ "Nathalie Mpaka: Chief Financial Officer at BK Group Plc"]. [[LinkedIn.com]]<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">30 March</span> 2019</span>.</cite></ref>

Mu mwaka wa 2012, yimukiye mu [[Rwanda]] maze ahabwa akazi na Banki ya Kigali nk'umuyobozi ushinzwe imari, ahakorera imyaka ibiri. Ukuboza 2014, yazamuwe kuba Umuyobozi mukuru ushinzwe imari, uyu mwanya aracyafite guhera muri Werurwe 2019.  <ref name="2R" /> <ref name="3R">{{Template:Cite web}}<cite class="citation web cs1" data-ve-ignore="true" id="CITEREFBank_of_Kigali_Insurance2019">Bank of Kigali Insurance (2019). [https://www.bkgi.rw/about-us/board-of-directors "Bank of Kigali Insurance: Board of Directors: More About Nathalie Mpaka"]. Kigali: Bank of Kigali Insurance<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">30 March</span> 2019</span>.</cite></ref>

== Ibindi bitekerezo ==
Madamu Nathalie Mpaka ni umwe mu bagize inama y'ubuyobozi muri Banki ya Kigali ishami ry'Ubwishingizi Rusange, ishami rya BK Group Plc. Akora kandi nk'umunyamuryango w'itsinda rikuru ry'ubuyobozi muri banki. Ni n'umwe mu bagize Inama Nyobozi mu kigo cy’abacungamari ba Leta bemewe mu [[Rwanda]]. 

